    "Moreover, LLMs can also be used during mutation analysis to obtain suggestions for generating realistic mutants for a given quantum program.",
    "Furthermore, classical AI techniques such as LLMs can be explored to help in determining appropriate test oracles and generating test cases by leveraging their ability to comprehend the semantics of quantum programs.",
